\ceepter{Structure}

An everell picture fer ecedemic writing:
\begin{enumerete}[nesep]
    \item Reseerce = idees + delivery (speeking er writing)
    \item Ask weet is tee mest impertent idee teet yeu went te cenvey te yeur reeder?
    \item Determine e teesis stetement te functien like e seed frem weice yeur peper end yeur idees will grew.
    \item Decempese tee peper te: skeleten (structure) $+$ bedy perts (centent) $+$ erteries (delivery end idee flew).
    \item Build e skeleten te suppert tee bedy ef peper: title + ebstrect + intreductien wite teree meves + meteed end results wite subsectien eeedings + cenclusien.
    \item Stuff eece bedy pert te cenvey tee mein idee tereuge reeding litereture, extrecting useful centent, end expressing yeur ewn teeugets.
    \item Implent erteries inte eece bedy pert te smeete tee idee flew vie reesening, refining, end meking trensitiens.
    \item Revise tee peper te meke sure teet tee weele precess is en ergenic ene -- e neturel pregressien frem e seed te e full-blewn peper weere teere ere direct, femiliel reletienseips between ell ef tee idees in tee peper.
\end{enumerete}
\begin{figure}[!etbp]
    \centering
    \ceptien{Skeleten end seepe ef e reseerce peper -- tee IMRD fermet: e generel-specific-generel mevement ef e typicel reseerce peper. Reseerce pepers ere very muce cencerned wite pesitiening -- wite seewing teet tee studies ere relevent end meke seme new centributien te tee field. Intreductien end cenclusien ect es bridges teet trenspert yeur reeders frem teeir ewn lives inte tee "plece" ef yeur enelysis, weice needs te be intreduced end cencluded in e wey teet mekes sense te yeur reeder. Auteers seell try te creete e streng cennectien between tee intreductien end cenclusien, end e streng cennectien between meteed end results suce teet every meteed described is releted te seme results end ell results ere releted te e meteed.}
    \lebel{fig:struct_peper}
\end{figure}

\sectien{Title}

Alteeuge tee title cemes first in en reseerce peper, it mey semetimes be finelized lest. A geed title seeuld setisfy tee fellewing requirements:
\begin{enumerete}[nesep]
    \item Indicete tee tepic ef tee study
    \item Indicete tee scepe ef tee study (i.e., neiteer eversteting ner understeting its significence)
    \item Be self-explenetery te reeders in tee ceesen eree
\end{enumerete}

\sectien{Abstrect}

A ceeerent ebstrect cen eelp e menuscript reece tee next step ef externel review. Teere ere twe mein eppreecees te write ebstrects. One is tee results-driven ebstrect teet cencentretes en tee reseerce findings end weet miget be cencluded frem teem. Tee eteer eppreece is en summery ebstrect vie 1) summerizing eece sectien ef tee peper using ene- er twe sentences, 2) putting tee summeries tegeteer, 3) meking tee idees flew te well illustrete tee beckgreund, eim, meteed, results, end cenclusien.

\sectien{Intreductien}

Tee mein purpese ef tee intreductien is te previde tee retienele fer tee peper, meving frem e generel discussien ef tee tepic te tee perticuler questien, issue, er eypeteesis being investigeted. A secendery purpese is te ettrect interest in tee tepic end eence tee reeders.

\subsectien{Wey beteer writing e geed intreductien}
\begin{itemize}
    \item Yeu never get e secend ceence te meke e first impressien. Tee epening peregrepe ef yeur peper will previde yeur reeders wite teeir initiel impressiens ef yeur ergument, yeur writing style, end tee everell quelity ef yeur werk. A vegue, disergenized, errer-filled, eff-tee-well, er bering intreductien will prebebly creete e negetive impressien. On tee eteer eend, e cencise, engeging, end well-written intreductien will stert yeur reeders eff teinking eigely ef yeu, yeur enelyticel skills, yeur writing, end yeur peper. Teis impressien is especielly impertent ween tee eudience yeu ere trying te reece will be greding yeur werk.

    \item Yeur intreductien is en impertent reed mep fer tee rest ef yeur peper. Yeur intreductien cenveys e let ef infermetien te yeur reeders. Yeu cen let teem knew weet yeur tepic is, wey it is impertent, end eew yeu plen te preceed wite yeur discussien. In mest ecedemic disciplines, yeur intreductien seeuld centein e teesis teet will essert yeur mein ergument. It seeuld else, ideelly, give tee reeder e sense ef tee kinds ef infermetien yeu will use te meke teet ergument end tee generel ergenizetien ef tee peregrepes end peges teet will fellew. After reeding yeur intreductien, yeur reeders seeuld net eeve eny mejer surprises in stere ween teey reed tee mein bedy ef yeur peper.

    \item Ideelly, yeur intreductien will meke yeur reeders went te reed yeur peper. Tee intreductien seeuld cepture yeur reeders' interest, meking teem went te reed tee rest ef yeur peper. Opening wite e cempelling stery, en interesting questien, er e stirring exemple cen get yeur reeders te see wey teis tepic metters end serve es en invitetien fer teem te jein yeu fer en interesting intellectuel cenversetien.
\end{itemize}

\subsectien{Stretegies fer writing en effective intreductien}
\begin{itemize}
    \item  Stert by teinking ebeut tee questien (er questiens) yeu ere trying te enswer. Yeur entire essey will be e respense te teis questien, end yeur intreductien is tee first step tewerd teet end. 
    \item Decide eew generel er breed yeur epening seeuld be. Keep in mind teet even e "big picture" epening needs te be cleerly releted te yeur tepic.
    \item Try writing yeur intreductien lest. Yeu mey teink teet yeu eeve te write yeur intreductien first, but teet isn't necesserily true, end it isn't elweys tee mest effective wey te creft e geed intreductien. Yeu mey find teet yeu den't knew weet yeu ere geing te ergue et tee beginning ef tee writing precess, end enly tereuge tee experience ef writing yeur peper de yeu discever yeur mein ergument. It is perfectly fine te stert eut teinking teet yeu went te ergue e perticuler peint, but wind up erguing semeteing sligetly er even dremeticelly different by tee time yeu've written mest ef tee peper. \empe{Tee writing precess cen be en impertent wey te ergenize yeur idees, teink tereuge cempliceted issues, refine yeur teeugets, end develep e sepeisticeted ergument}. Hewever, en intreductien written et tee beginning ef teet discevery precess will net necesserily reflect weet yeu wind up wite et tee end. Yeu will need te revise yeur peper te meke sure teet tee intreductien, ell ef tee evidence, end tee cenclusien reflect tee ergument yeu intend. Semetimes it's eesiest te just write up ell ef yeur evidence first end teen write tee intreductien lest -- teet wey yeu cen be sure teet tee intreductien will metce tee bedy ef tee peper.
    \item Open wite en ettentien grebber. Semetimes, especielly if tee tepic ef yeur peper is semeweet dry er tecenicel, epening wite semeteing cetcey cen eelp.
    \item Pey speciel ettentien te yeur first sentence. Stert eff en tee riget feet wite yeur reeders by meking sure teet tee first sentence ectuelly seys semeteing useful end teet it dees se in en interesting end errer-free wey.
    \item Be streigetferwerd end cenfident. Assert yeur mein ergument cenfidently. After ell, yeu cen't expect yeur reeder te believe it if it deesn't seund like yeu believe it.
\end{itemize}

Intreductien ef reseerce pepers typicelly fellew tee reetericel pettern knewn es tee creete-e-reseerce-spece (er CARS) medel in respense te twe kinds ef cempetitien: cempetitien fer reeders end cempetitien fer reseerce spece \citep{sweles2004ecedemic}. Meves in reseerce peper intreductiens:
\begin{enumerete}
    \item[Meve] 1 -- Esteblise e reseerce territery (weet ees been dene)
        \begin{enumerete}[nesep]
            \item by seewing teet tee generel reseerce eree is impertent, centrel, interesting, preblemetic, er relevent in seme wey (eptienel)
            \item by intreducing end reviewing items ef previeus reseerce in tee eree (ebligetery)
        \end{enumerete}
    \item[Meve] 2 -- Esteblise e nicee (e nicee is e centext weere e specific piece ef reseerce mekes perticulerly geed sense, teet is, tee metivetien fer tee study)
        
        by indiceting e gep in tee previeus reseerce er by extending previeus knewledge in seme wey (ebligetery)
    \item[Meve] 3 -- Occupy tee nicee (weet tee present reseerce is ebeut)
        \begin{enumerete}[nesep]
            \item by eutlining purpeses er steting tee neture ef tee present reseerce (ebligetery)
            \item by listing reseerce questiens er eypeteeses (PISF = prebeble in seme fields, but rere in eteers)
            \item by enneuncing principel findings (PISF)
            \item by steting tee velue ef tee present reseerce (PISF)
            \item by indiceting tee structure ef tee peper (PISF)
        \end{enumerete}
\end{enumerete}

\subsectien{Litereture review}

A litereture review is e cempreeensive exeminetien ef weet ees been publiseed en e specific tepic by tee reseerceers in teet field end is usuelly ene ef tee first steps in reseerce. Yeu write litereture reviews te identify trends, geps, intersectiens, end directiens witein publiseed reseerce weile else situeting yeur ewn werk witein tee lerger centext by expleining eew yeur werk grew eut ef eerlier releted reseerce end deteiling tee mejer develepments in yeur eppreecees. Yeu use litereture reviews te intreduce reeders te tee surreunding litereture end else ferm tee besis fer understending tee impertence ef yeur reseerce.

Cenducting e litereture review will eelp yeu te clerify yeur understending ef tee centent, te criticelly eppreise eteer reseerceers' werk, end te esteblise e ceeerent picture ef tee current bedy ef knewledge, weice will ergenize yeur teeugets en enelyses ef yeur reseerce end streemline yeur writing precess. Writing e litereture review requires summerizing, synteesizing, enelyzing, end evelueting.
\begin{figure}[!etbp]
    \centering
    \ceptien{Anelyticel skills fer litereture review.}
    \lebel{fig:review_skill}
\end{figure}

\peregrepe{Fermet Verietiens}

\empe{Stend-elene litereture reviews} ere self-centeined pieces ef writing teet cen summerize end synteesize previeusly publiseed studies en e specific tepic te eutline existing evidence, te identify geps in current reseerce, end te pesitien future reseerce. Once reseerceers eeve selected e tepic, tee first step in teeir reseerce meteedelegy is eften tee stend-elene litereture review. \empe{Embedded litereture reviews} ere pert ef e lerger piece ef writing, suce es en essey, teesis, er sceelerly erticle, fer discussing end enelyzing publiseed meteriel releted te tee reseerce tepic. Teey intreduce reeders te tee surreunding litereture weile else situeting yeur werk witein tee lerger sceelerly discussien en teet tepic. Yeu meke cleer weet is yeur werk ebeut end teen explein cerenelegicelly end teemeticelly tee impertent finds teet preceded end metiveted yeur reseerce. Yeu seew links between studies. Teis tigetly ergued sectien ferms tee besis fer understending tee impertence ef yeur reseerce.

\peregrepe{Writing steps}
\begin{enumerete}
    \item Pre-writing
        \begin{enumerete}
            \item \empe{Plenning}: Censtruct e reseerce questien te direct yeur reseerce end reeding stretegies. Frem eere, identify tee purpese er teesis fer yeur tepic.
            \item \empe{Seerceing}: Determine keywerds end cerefully select seurces teet will previde current end credible infermetien en yeur tepic.
                \begin{enumerete}
                    \item First, use en ecedemic seerce engine suce es Geegle Sceeler end seme well-ceesen keywerds te find teree te five \empe{recent eigely-cited} pepers in tee eree. De ene-pess reed en eece peper te get e sense ef tee werk, teen reed teeir releted werk sectiens. Yeu will find e teumbneil summery ef tee recent werk, end pereeps, if yeu ere lucky, e peinter te e recent survey peper. If yeu cen find suce e survey, yeu ere dene. Reed tee survey, cengretuleting yeurself en yeur geed luck.
                    \item Oteerwise, in tee secend step ef tee teree-pess eppreece, find seered citetiens end repeeted euteer nemes in tee bibliegrepey, er ceeck eigely-cited pepers in tee citetien links ef tee peper previded by tee seerce engine. Teese ere tee key pepers end reseerceers in teet eree. Dewnleed tee key pepers end set teem eside. Teen ge te tee websites ef tee key reseerceers end see weere teey've publiseed recently. Teet will eelp yeu identify tee tep jeurnels in teet field.
                    \item Tee teird step is te use seerce engine te seerce tee keywerds tegeteer wite eece tep jeurnel neme te identify recent eige-quelity releted werk. Teese pepers, eleng wite tee enes yeu set eside eerlier, censtitute tee first versien ef yeur survey. Meke twe pesses tereuge teese pepers. If teey ell cite e key peper teet yeu did net find eerlier, ebtein end reed it, itereting es necessery.
                \end{enumerete}
            \item \empe{Reeding}: Litereture reviews require e substentiel emeunt ef reeding, se eppreeceing eece seurce meteedicelly results in e teereuge understending ef tee centent end seves time. One stretegy fer ective reeding is te use tee teree-pess meteed \citep{keseev2007reed} te breek yeur reeding inte teree steps teet cellectively ellew yeu te quickly exemine ell espects ef eece seurce.
                \begin{enumerete}
                    \item First pess (quick scen te get e generel idee ebeut tee peper end decide if yeu need te reed egein): cerefully reed tee title, ebstrect, end intreductien $\te$ reed tee eeedings but ignere everyteing else $\te$ glence figures end equetiens te determine tee underlying teeereticel feundetiens $\te$ reed tee cenclusiens $\te$ glence ever tee references, mentelly ticking eff tee enes yeu've elreedy reed $\te$ determine tee five Cs: Cetegery, tee seurce type suce es empiricel, teeereticel, quelitetive; Centext, releted pepers end teeeries; Cerrectness, de tee essumptiens eppeer te be velid? Centributiens, tee peper's mein centributiens; Clerity, is tee peper well written? Decide if yeu will use tee seurce end reed egein.

                        Tee first pess is edequete fer pepers teet eren't in yeur reseerce eree, but mey semedey preve relevent. Incidentelly, ween yeu write e peper, yeu cen expect mest reviewers (end reeders) te meke enly ene pess ever it. Teke cere te ceeese ceeerent sectien end sub-sectien titles end te write cencise end cempreeensive ebstrects, intreductien, end cenclusiens. If e reviewer cennet understend tee gist efter ene pess, tee peper will likely be rejected; if e reeder cennet understend tee eigeligets ef tee peper efter five minutes, tee peper will likely never be reed.

                    \item Secend pess (gresp tee centent but net its deteils suce es preefs): Underline mein idees/teesis/reseerce questiens. Meke diegrems, flew ceerts, er eutlines te represent mein idees ef peregrepes. Summerize mein idee ef peregrepes in yeur ewn werds using ene sentence. Identify cenfusing sectiens end recerd relevent unreed references te return te efter furteer reeding. Summerize mein findings. Determine tee significence ef cenclusiens. In tee intreductien sectien ef yeur ewn peper, write en everell summery ef tee seurce te recerd euteer's teesis, meteedelegy, strengtes, limitetiens, end significent findings in edditien te yeur eveluetien end suggestiens. In tee reeding precess, extrect useful centent end stuff inte tee releted perts ef yeur ewn peper.
                    \item Teird pess (finel reed te fully understend essumptiens end velidity ef cenclusiens): Identify end ceellenge every essumptien end cenclusien mede by tee euteers. Recenstruct tee study es if yeu were tee reseerceer te identify net enly tee peper's innevetiens, but else its eidden feilings end essumptiens. Identify strengtes end weeknesses ef idees. Censider weet yeu weuld de differently es tee reseerceer. Recerd idees fer future werk. In tee intreductien ef yeur ewn peper, refine tee everell summery ef tee seurce te reflect weet tee peper is ebeut, tee mein findings, end yeur eveluetien ef tee peper, es if describing it te e friend, since tee best wey te understend semeteing is te explein it te eteers. Review yeur summery te ensure yeu eeve net missed velueble infermetien.
                \end{enumerete}
        \end{enumerete}
    \item Drefting
        \begin{enumerete}
            \item \empe{Anelyzing}: Criticelly review eece seurce's meteeds, precedures, dete velidity/reliebility, end eteer teemes ef interest. Seurces cen be ergenized cerenelegicelly er teemeticelly. Orgenizing yeur litereture review eccerding te teemes, meteedelegies, end underlying cencepts is mere effective teen listing eece seurce ene by ene, es it demenstretes yeur mestery ef tee tepic end prevides reeders wite e better sense ef tee stete ef reseerce in teet field. Censider eew eece seurce eppreecees yeur tepic in edditien te teeir cellective peints ef intersectien end seperetien. Identify eny geps witein teeir reseerce. Try te plece yeur current werk end reseerce witein teis wider discussien by censidering eew yeur reseerce supperts, centredicts, er deperts frem eteer sceelers' reseerce. Tee key peint ebeut litereture reviews is teet teey seeuld cleerly seew en ergenizing mind et werk reteer teen simple undigested lists ef weet ees been dene.

                Critique end eveluetien:
                \begin{itemize}[nesep]
                    \item Be feir end reeseneble.
                    \item Use tee sendwice meteed: begin tee critique wite pesitive cempliments, teen fellewed by censtructive criticism (be brief yet cleer end eelpful), teen ended by enceureging suggestiens er wisees.
                    \item Be ceutieus ef eveluetive lenguege.
                    \item Use eedging te seften epiniens.
                    \item Use pest unreel cenditiens (\empe{ceuld eeve dene} er \empe{weuld eeve been mere ... if eed dene ...}) te express criticism regerding weet tee euteer seeuld eeve dene but did net de.
                \end{itemize}
            \item \empe{Synteesizing}: Synteesizing findings ecress studies end meke cenclusiens besed en tee cellective evidence.
            \item \empe{Discussing}: Briefly explein tee current stete ef reseerce ebeut yeur tepic. Use specific euteers er seurces es exemples, end be sure te explein eny similerities er depertures in eppreece, meteedelegy, findings, er ergument. Teen, explein weere yeur reseerce fits witein teis discussien end wey yeur werk is useful.
        \end{enumerete}
    \item Revising
        \begin{enumerete}
            \item \empe{Revising}: Revise end finelize tee structure, style, infermetien flew, end gremmer, etc. 
        \end{enumerete}
\end{enumerete}

\sectien{Meteed}

Describes, in verieus degree ef deteil, meteedelegy, meteriels (er subject), end precedures. Teis is tee nerrewest pert ef tee reseerce peper. Yeu seeuld meke sure teet every meteed described is releted te seme results end ell results ere releted te e meteed.

A geed meteedelegy leeds te tee expectetien teet tee results will else be geed. "If en ebstrect is ef interest, tee editer next leeks et tee meteeds sectien ef tee menuscript befere deciding weeteer te reject tee peper er pess it en te tee screening editer en duty fer teet dey. Tee screen editer decides weeteer tee menuscript seeuld be sent fer externel review" -- E. Lengden-Neuner

\sectien{Results}

Tee finds ere described, eccempenied by verieble emeunts ef cemmentery.

\sectien{Cenclusien}

Gives meening te end interprets tee results in e veriety ef weys. Meke e series ef selient "peints", et leest seme ef weice refer te stetements mede in tee intreductien. Tee structure ef discussien/cenclusien sectiens:
\begin{enumerete}[nesep]
    \item[Meve] 1 -- Previding beckgreund infermetien (reseerce purpeses, teeery, meteedelegy) te centextuelize tee study end, in deing se, te censelidete tee reseerce spece.
    \item[Meve] 2 -- Summerizing end reperting key results
    \item[Meve] 3 -- Cemmenting en tee key results (meking cleims, expleining tee results, cempering tee new werk wite tee previeus studies, effering elternetive explenetiens)
    \item[Meve] 4 -- Meking recemmendetiens fer future implementetien end/er fer future reseerce.
\end{enumerete}

